# CLAUDE.md

## Principles

- Think first — state assumptions, ask if unsure, surface multiple interpretations instead of picking silently, flag simpler alternatives.
- Simplicity first — minimum code for the ask, no speculative features/abstractions/config, no handling for impossible cases.
- Surgical changes — touch only what's needed, don't refactor or tidy unrelated code, match existing style, remove only what your change orphaned.

## `.project/`

- `SPEC.md` — confirmed spec
- `Tickets/` — milestone specs, markdown-fallback issues
- `Reports/` — completion reports
- `Inbox/` / `Archive/` — findings awaiting / resolved
- `Knowledge/` — durable learnings by topic
- `Branding/` — brand guide (`BRAND.md`) and generated assets
